        <sect1>
            <title>Yali, Goddess of Passion</title>

            <para>
                Yali won the <qv 
                uri="belogan-wisdoms">Wisdoms</qv> of beauty, 
                love and passion. She is the goddess of true 
                love, not the crude pleasure  of sex (which is 
                enjoyed by <qv uri="koros">Koros</qv>).
            </para>

